[
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p000.jpg",
    "text": "TA]"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p001.jpg",
    "text": "We're so screwed:_"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p002.jpg",
    "text": "Infirmary"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p003.jpg",
    "text": "HOw DARE YOU CAUSE s0 MUCH RACKET WHILE CLASSES ARE STiLL GOINGI?\nT'M SENDING YOU TwO"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p004.jpg",
    "text": "StrAiGHT to KEENE AFTER thiS}\nLook Doc, Iwas just minding my own business, studying: Then he comes over and punches me out of nowhere:\nJwyare"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p005.jpg",
    "text": "Really, Blyke?\nYou know that wouldn't have happened if you hadn't broken my pen:\n~\n6"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p006.jpg",
    "text": "Me AudH! GIVE IT WAS BREAK? THE MOST USELESS PART OF THE PEN?\nDON'T\nCARE? DON'T BREAK MY STUFF'\nShut up_"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p007.jpg",
    "text": "It doesn't matter who started the fight:\nOuch that hurts__"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p008.jpg",
    "text": "Ijust want you two to understand that your actions have conseq-\nDoc._"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p009.jpg",
    "text": "Yeiel"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p010.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p011.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p012.jpg",
    "text": "WORDINARY Episode 6"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p013.jpg",
    "text": "Wosla Beba"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p014.jpg",
    "text": "EMBER GANG STRIKES AGAIN\nOf all things, you threw him out of window?\nWell; it's not like had-"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p015.jpg",
    "text": "HEY! THAT'S NOT FUNNY!\nS Creatle\nCOULD'VE BEEN KILLED?\nYou always say that:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p016.jpg",
    "text": "Yet here you are again ,=\nStill in one piece.\nYou're missing the point:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p017.jpg",
    "text": "Come on, it's gotta be at least a little exciting'\nLiving on the edge seems So fun?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p018.jpg",
    "text": "Not at all:.\nreally just want moment of peace:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p019.jpg",
    "text": "Right now, every little conflict always turns into a full on brawl:\nIcan't do anything with- out fearing for my lifel\nWhy does the world have to be so violent?\nWhat's wrong with talking things over with one another?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p020.jpg",
    "text": "Because it's a waste of time_\nThere's no need to argue with a weakling to prove a point__"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p021.jpg",
    "text": "Because you can just overpower him?\nThe stronger person isn't always right; you know?\nTo have to use force to back up your"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p022.jpg",
    "text": "claim:_. it's so pathetic'\nWhat are you implying?\nAh:."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p023.jpg",
    "text": "didn't mean you; just high-tiers in general"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p024.jpg",
    "text": "JGNbRe"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p025.jpg",
    "text": "Sera was born strong."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p026.jpg",
    "text": "So she doesn't understand what people like me\nhave to go through every day-."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p027.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p028.jpg",
    "text": "~presence: EMBER has been leaving a trail of bodies The most recent one being in Lovun:\nIn an alley, near the intersection of Rokel and Acres Street:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p029.jpg",
    "text": "Investigators have identified the body as the well known vigilante, \"X-Static\". No further personal information was given:\nBreaking news: 'EMBER' GANG STRIKES AGAIN"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p030.jpg",
    "text": "The victim's body was covered in second degree burns and multiple stab wounds:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p031.jpg",
    "text": "And like all other EMBER victims,\nA very promiment brand of its logo marked the corpse:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p032.jpg",
    "text": "Lovun? That's the next town over!\nCould EMBER be heading here?\nPuh? X-Static. How useless?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p033.jpg",
    "text": "Hm:.."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p034.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p035.jpg",
    "text": "And yet another self- proclaimed \"Superhero\"\nFalls victim to the consequences of every day society_"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p036.jpg",
    "text": "People need to learn to mind their own business\nEspecially if they don't have the strength to back it up."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p037.jpg",
    "text": "But he was trying to keep us safe."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p038.jpg",
    "text": "Doyou feel safer\nSuRP"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p039.jpg",
    "text": "Now that he's dead?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p040.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_7\\unordinary_ep7_p041.jpg",
    "text": "unORDINARY - Episode 6 [end]\n@uru:chan\n@uruchanOFR Gutttec\nMolagrar"
  },
